  <h1>Follistatin 344: Guide to Myostatin Inhibition and Muscle Growth</h1>
  <p class="sub">A naturally occurring glycoprotein that binds myostatin and activins, studied for its role in muscle development. What the research shows, what it doesn't, and how to think about this compound honestly.</p>
  <div class="pills">
